{"id": "ChIJaYaK-g7Z3IARq8wH8ORaODU", "rating": 4.6, "userRatingCount": 55, "displayName": {"text": "Pan y Café Panaderia", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJaYaK-g7Z3IARq8wH8ORaODU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aeWEzRTBlbFJHY2tkMFIwUkhjMWQwYnpkS09WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "1. The pastries were delicious! The coffee was well-crafted!\n2. The spot has fun casual vibes! The interior is nicely arranged!\n3. The staff was friendly and timely with my order! My coffee was ready after 5 mins!\nNote: I did not see a restroom available for customers!\n\nPhoto: Horchata Latte, Rollo De Mora, and Puerquito", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "1. The pastries were delicious! The coffee was well-crafted!\n2. The spot has fun casual vibes! The interior is nicely arranged!\n3. The staff was friendly and timely with my order! My coffee was ready after 5 mins!\nNote: I did not see a restroom available for customers!\n\nPhoto: Horchata Latte, Rollo De Mora, and Puerquito", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Andy Vu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107058405522234792971/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM7eqOVi2qqP-FLPL_I7l01i_UC0CeUJw0mmnuNh8j2WNuFGYK=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-21T03:10:30.586131355Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aeWEzRTBlbFJHY2tkMFIwUkhjMWQwYnpkS09WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aeWEzRTBlbFJHY2tkMFIwUkhjMWQwYnpkS09WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dcd90efa8a8669:0x35385ae4f007ccab"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaYaK-g7Z3IARq8wH8ORaODU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkeVNuYzFOR1pzV21aVmMweFlaV3R3V1VKUGVuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Pan y Café brings that warm, neighborhood bakery comfort with a modern, cozy vibe. Fresh pastries come out tasting like they were made with real care soft, buttery, and perfect with their smooth, well\nbalanced coffee. It’s the kind of spot where you can slow down for a minute, enjoy something sweet, and feel taken care of by the friendly staff. A simple, feel good stop that always hits right.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Pan y Café brings that warm, neighborhood bakery comfort with a modern, cozy vibe. Fresh pastries come out tasting like they were made with real care soft, buttery, and perfect with their smooth, well\nbalanced coffee. It’s the kind of spot where you can slow down for a minute, enjoy something sweet, and feel taken care of by the friendly staff. A simple, feel good stop that always hits right.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "FELIX Barajas", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111374006686243022973/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5WJOzsuzR45lrrIiYjXoIiLKs7oXvHgQIBYsjTjKq8AgX=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-26T22:44:48.434905305Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkeVNuYzFOR1pzV21aVmMweFlaV3R3V1VKUGVuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkeVNuYzFOR1pzV21aVmMweFlaV3R3V1VKUGVuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80dcd90efa8a8669:0x35385ae4f007ccab"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaYaK-g7Z3IARq8wH8ORaODU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25NM1YyUkhSR3RZZEhKQ1NXczNkV0ZUT0RFMWJXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "this bakery should have over 20,000 + 5 stars because today the chocolate concha was better than the one I ate growing up. the bread without the cookie part ontop alone was so good and paired with cookie part took me to the rocketed me to the moon. everything there looked just beautiful 